OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FHere is everything we know about the
OL,7,Finvestigation so far.
OL,9,FWho are Legacy Independent Funeral
OL,10,FDirectors?
OL,12,FAccording to its website, Legacy is a
OL,13,F"family business", led by funeral
OL,14,Fdirector and owner, Robert Bush.
OL,16,FEstablished in 2010, it expanded from
OL,17,Fits original branch on Anlaby Road in
OL,18,FHull to incorporate two further
OL,19,Fbranches ` a funeral home in Beverley
OL,20,Fand another on Hessle Road, Hull.
