OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,F"Our structure allows us to provide a
OL,7,Fdedicated and unsurpassed personal
OL,8,Fservice," the website says.
OL,10,F"As an independent funeral director,
OL,11,Fwe are able to create a unique
OL,12,Ffarewell for loved ones, with more
OL,13,Fflexibility and less constraint than
OL,14,Four competitors."
OL,16,FThe business is thought to have been a
OL,17,Fmember of the professional body, the
OL,18,FNational Association of Funeral
OL,19,FDirectors (NAFD), from 2011 but gave
OL,20,Fup its membership in 2021.
