OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FWhat prompted the investigation?
OL,8,FOn Wednesday, 6 March, a report was
OL,9,Fmade to police expressing concern
OL,10,Fabout the "storage and management
OL,11,Fprocesses relating to the care of the
OL,12,Fdeceased" at various locations run by
OL,13,FLegacy Funeral Directors.
OL,15,FPolice said that several enquiries
OL,16,Fwere made afterwards to "ascertain the
OL,17,Fexact details, concern and
OL,18,Fcircumstances".
