OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FA team of detectives started working
OL,7,Fwith partner agencies including Hull
OL,8,FCity Council, East Riding of Yorkshire
OL,9,FCouncil and His Majesty's Coroner.
OL,11,FOn Friday, 8 March, police said
OL,12,Fcordons were in place at all three
OL,13,Fsites.
OL,15,FA direct phone line was set up for
OL,16,Fanyone with concerns.
