OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FHull West and Hessle MP Emma Hardy
OL,7,Fsaid she was "extremely shocked" at
OL,8,Fthe investigation and could "only
OL,9,Fimagine the distress and devastation"
OL,10,Ffamilies felt.
OL,12,FA day later, on 9 March, Humberside
OL,13,FPolice confirmed it was in the process
OL,14,Fof moving "a number of deceased" from
OL,15,Fthe premises on Hessle Road to the
OL,16,Fcouncil's mortuary.
OL,18,FWhat are the allegations?
