OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FTwo people ` a 46-year-old man and a
OL,7,F23-year-old woman ` have been arrested
OL,8,Fon suspicion of prevention of a lawful
OL,9,Fand decent burial, fraud by false
OL,10,Frepresentation and fraud by abuse of
OL,11,Fposition.
OL,13,FThey have since been released on bail.
OL,15,FPolice have not been specific about
OL,16,Fthe nature of the alleged offences,
OL,17,Fbut have described what has happened
OL,18,Fas a "truly horrific incident".
