OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FDeputy Chief Constable David Marshall
OL,7,Ftold a press conference on 12 March:
OL,8,F"This is an extremely complex and
OL,9,Fsensitive investigation, with
OL,10,Fheartbroken and devastated families at
OL,11,Fthe core of it."
OL,13,FAssistant Chief Constable Thom
OL,14,FMcLoughlin told families "we will do
OL,15,Feverything we possibly can to give you
OL,16,Fthe answers you deserve".
OL,18,FHow many people are affected?
