OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FPolice said they had moved 35 bodies
OL,7,Ffrom the business's premises to the
OL,8,Fcity's mortuary.
OL,10,FThe force said a "quantity" of
OL,11,Fsuspected human ashes had also been
OL,12,Frecovered and were being
OL,13,F"respectfully" moved.
OL,15,FOn Friday, 15 March, the force said it
OL,16,Fhad contacted the families of the 35
OL,17,Fpeople whose bodies had been moved.
