OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FIn a follow-up press conference on 4
OL,7,FApril, officers said they were unable
OL,8,Fto identify any of the ashes that had
OL,9,Fbeen recovered because of the loss of
OL,10,FDNA.
OL,12,FMore than 2,000 calls have been made
OL,13,Fto the dedicated phone line.
OL,15,FMore than 120 officers and civilian
OL,16,Fstaff are working on the case
OL,17,Falongside experts from the National
OL,18,FCrime Agency.
