OL,3,CFuneral directors investigation: What
OL,4,Cdo we know so far?
OL,6,FHull City Council said affected
OL,7,Ffamilies would not have to pay for new
OL,8,Ffunerals for their loved ones.
OL,10,FWhat about other funeral businesses?
OL,12,FHull City Council said checks had been
OL,13,Fcarried out at 50 funeral directors in
OL,14,Fthe wake of the investigation into
OL,15,FLegacy.
OL,17,FThe local authority say it was "very
OL,18,Fclear" the investigation was "in no
OL,19,Fway typical" of wider problems in the
OL,20,Findustry in the area.
